headline: Cummins Announces Appointment of Nicole Y. Lamb-Hale as Chief Administrative Officer and Corporate Secretary
summary: COLUMBUS, Ind., April 02, 2025--Cummins Inc. (NYSE: CMI) announced today that Nicole Y. Lamb-Hale has been appointed Chief Administrative Officer and Corporate Secretary, effective June 1. She will succeed Sharon Barner when she retires on May 31.
